{"title":"ERROR_ ‘_usr_sbin_iptables-restore -w -n‘ failed_ iptables-restore v1.8.2 (nf_tables)","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.057Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/ERROR_ ‘_usr_sbin_iptables-restore -w -n‘ failed_ iptables-restore v1.8.2 (nf_tables)","updated":"2023-07-28T09:19:48.126Z","content":"<p>最近配置了防火墙端口，用firewall-cmd --reload操作无效<br>\n始终报如下的错误</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ERROR: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;/usr/sbin/iptables-restore -w -n&#x27;</span> failed: iptables<span class=\"literal\">-restore</span> v1.<span class=\"number\">8.2</span> (nf_tables): </span><br><span class=\"line\">                                                          line <span class=\"number\">4</span>: RULE_REPLACE failed (No such file or directory): rule <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> chain INPUT</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                                          line <span class=\"number\">4</span>: RULE_REPLACE failed (No such file or directory): rule <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> chain OUTPUT</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>解决方法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim /etc/firewalld/firewalld.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>找到</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">IndividualCalls=no</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#把no改为yes</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/c31aaf97e68e494891451a7139bd76a6.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n按<code>esc</code>，输入<code>:wq</code>保存退出<br>\n然后重启firewalld服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl restart firewalld.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>重启之后即可正常执行firewall-cmd --reload</p>\n","prev":{"title":"ERROR 1819 (HY000)_ Your password does not satisfy the current policy requirements","link":"2023/07/28/ERROR 1819 (HY000)_ Your password does not satisfy the current policy requirements"},"next":{"title":"Eclipse配置Go语言环境，并运行第一个Go项目","link":"2023/07/28/Eclipse配置Go语言环境，并运行第一个Go项目"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/ERROR_ ‘_usr_sbin_iptables-restore -w -n‘ failed_ iptables-restore v1.8.2 (nf_tables)/","reading_time":"140 字约 1 分钟"}